---
title: Speedy BBQ Tofu and Pepper Braised Beans with Buttery Toasties
description: This one is for all the braised bean enthusiasts. Sweet and smoky BBQ charred tofu adorns the quickest braised beans you've ever made. It's served up with ciabatta toasties to help mop up all that goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-bbq-et-haricots-braises-aux-piments-17936174.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/speedy-bbq-tofu-and-pepper-braised-beans-65a6444fd927ae782706fc0b-5ddc4c0a.pdf
